one_reviews_text: Finally an exhibit where you can grab the art (and other things) and play with it. Could use a little more polish, and I didn’t succeed in opening the door (I  think I needed an object that seemed to be missing?)
Not what I expected, Very Interactive and fun, Expect a bit of a challenge too with certain areas. Solve Puzzles to open other areas. So creative, Thank you
review_feedback: Thank you for your comment Mushroomies. We love that you like the experience.

review_title: A quirky lil experience, not a gallery.
one_reviews_text: Weird, in a good way. I was hoping for more arts, but this is unique and odd and cool.
Seems unfinished, not very enlightening, and boring.
concept seem fun, but feels unfinished...
